Prof Nabel is very Knowledgeable about his field. The course may seem like a lot but taking this class with him will give you an opportunity to tap into his wealth of Knowledge. Project was good and the idea was "to learn". Midterms and Finals were average in terms of difficulty. I would recommend him if you love a to learn and value a challenge.

rComments: Uploads both hand written and typed notes. Makes resources easy to access. This course had a midterm, a final, and 4 quizzes (of which he only takes the best 3 for the final grade). Every year he changes up the material which is nice. He covered PDEs which was interesting and he's always happy to answer questions and extremely helpful. Attend class because he'll cover examples!!!!!
